prod.desciption:
The Nike Dunk Low SP UNDEFEATED Canteen features a Canteen canvas and leather upper with a Palomino canvas toe wrap and eyestay. Lemon Frost leather Swooshes and UNDEFEATED tally mark insignias on the tongue, heel tab, and lateral heel complete the design.

The Nike Dunk Low SP UNDEFEATED Canteen released in June of 2021 and retailed for $120.
